&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; thanks for your help.
&gt; 
&gt; one final question, is it ok to model the API for &#39;status&#39; as 
&gt; http://example. org/openQRM/ service/abc123# status 
&gt; &lt;http://example.org/openQRM/service/abc123#status&gt; (thus stating more 
